videos.description: Kaiser Gates penetrates to the basket and dishes it to Tyrique Jones for the slam.
videos.headline: Xavier connection ends with dunk

videos.description: Naji Marshall dishes it to Sean O'Mara for the two-handed hammer.
videos.headline: Xavier's O'Mara flushes it down

videos.description: Quentin Goodin drives to the basket and double pumps for the tough finish and-1.
videos.headline: Xavier's Goodin helps cut into lead with and-1

videos.description: Kerem Kanter comes off the screen and hits the game-tying three-pointer to tie the game at 66.
videos.headline: Musketeers' Kanter ties the game

videos.description: Trevon Bluiett pulls up with three defenders in his face and knocks down the game-winning jumper as Xavier beats ETSU 68-66.
videos.headline: Xavier's Bluiett has ice-water in his veins
